                            <div id="description" itemprop="description">
                                <h1>Von - Minimalist Blog Theme</h1>
<p>Von is a minimalist blog theme, designed to optimize your reading experience as much as possible. With support for mobile and tablet devices you can easily reach all your readers.</p>
<h1>Features</h1>
<ul>
<li>Minimal &amp; Lightweight</li>
<li>Bootstrap 3.1</li>
<li>Font Awesome</li>
<li>Google Fonts</li>
<li>Easy customizable</li>
<li>HTML5 &amp; CSS3</li>
<li>SEO Optimized</li>
<li>Cross browser</li>
<li>Disqus</li>
<li>Have a question? Ask me!</li>
</ul>
<h1>Changelog</h1>
<h3>1.01 - 31-01-2014</h3>
<ul>
<li>Upgraded to Bootstrap 3.1</li>
<li>Upgraded to jQuery 1.11.0</li>
<li>Sidebar vertical scrollable</li>
</ul>
